{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We take the ferry from [INAUDIBLE] and we go all the way through and we-- we get on a ferry boat in Copenhagen and the next stop is Malmo, Sweden.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for all practical purpose, my war was over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We get assigned to a resort hotel which was empty at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And oh, I had that bathtub.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I laid in that bathtub for I don't know how many hours, I guess to try to get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the next day, we had some of the Jewish people came out there and got us clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a suit and got a couple of shirts, some underwear things, like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so now we looked like human people, like humans again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all-- we were all skinny in a sense, but we-- we survived, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and so we stayed in Sweden there till-- they had a Danish brigade there at that time they were forming of Danish underground people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we a bunch of us said, we'd like to join the brigade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at that time, they said, it's too late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are looking to get over there to Germany and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they didn't take us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Plus, we weren't in that kind of shape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we had that kind of a hate left, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So about on the 15th of May, the war was over about eight days already, we get back to Denmark, right.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By they shipped us back, right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Swedish take us back on a ferry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time we get a sign for a short time, somebody-- big families in Denmark sort of adopt us for a short time, not for long.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I was assigned to the agricultural minister.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
